focused, getting together,

00:37:39.840 --> 00:37:44.120
and not taking that instinctive
reaction of, you know,

00:37:44.120 --> 00:37:47.240
sort of irritation or
grumpiness that you often get

00:37:47.240 --> 00:37:50.420
and using that opportunity
to tone things down,

00:37:50.420 --> 00:37:53.700
that's actually made
people a lot more receptive

00:37:53.700 --> 00:37:55.700
to what I'm asking them to do.

00:37:55.700 --> 00:37:57.930
