with teammates in London,

00:38:00.434 --> 00:38:01.850
teammates in
California, teammates

00:38:01.850 --> 00:38:04.710
in other parts of the world.

00:38:04.710 --> 00:38:07.095
And that for me has been a
big improvement, definitely.

00:38:07.095 --> 00:38:08.220
DAVID GELLES: That's great.

